            "bg_color": "#44aade",
            "text": {
                "header": "Nice Work!",
                "body": "<p>You did it! Pricing approvals aren't that scary. And with resources like Slingshot to keep you in the clear, it should make sales planning a cinch!</p><p>If you want any practice with pricing approvals before working on a real campaign, don't sweat it! Just practice in our Slingshot training environment! </p>",
                "class": "align-right"
